### 3. Delete Model Endpoint Handler

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775466918452-al1ud3/server/routes.go` (Lines 1055-1104)

